Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.Network.Server

Interface VisitorServer

All Known Implementing Classes:
VisitorMethodsServer
public interface VisitorServer
Each incoming message is sent here. The type of the message is analysed and the right method is sent to VisitorMethodsServer
